---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Savings Goal Calculator
description: Estimate the monthly contribution needed to reach a future savings goal based on current savings, time, and expected investment return.
navKey: tools
tags: tools
scripts:
  - /assets/tools/savings-goal.js
---

<div class="calculator-page">
    <section class="page-hero page-hero-compact">
        <p class="eyebrow">Planning ahead</p>

        <h1>Savings Goal Calculator</h1>

        <p class="hero-copy">
            Estimate how much you may need to contribute each month
            to reach a future savings goal.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section
        class="calculator-card"
        data-savings-goal-calculator
        aria-label="Savings goal calculator"
    >
        <div class="calculator-input-grid">
            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="savingsGoal">
                    Future savings goal
                </label>

                <input
                    id="savingsGoal"
                    type="number"
                    min="0.01"
                    step="any"
                    value="100000"
                    inputmode="decimal"
                >
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="currentSavings">
                    Current savings
                </label>

                <input
                    id="currentSavings"
                    type="number"
                    min="0"
                    step="any"
                    value="10000"
                    inputmode="decimal"
                >
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="savingsReturn">
                    Expected annual return after fees
                </label>

                <div class="calculator-input-suffix">
                    <input
                        id="savingsReturn"
                        type="number"
                        min="0"
                        max="100"
                        step="0.01"
                        value="5"
                        inputmode="decimal"
                    >

                    <span aria-hidden="true">%</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-field">
                <label for="savingsYears">
                    Number of years
                </label>

                <input
                    id="savingsYears"
                    type="number"
                    min="1"
                    max="100"
                    step="1"
                    value="10"
                    inputmode="numeric"
                >
            </div>
        </div>

        <p
            class="calculator-error"
            id="savingsGoalError"
            role="alert"
        ></p>

        <div
            class="calculator-results"
            aria-live="polite"
        >
            <div class="calculator-result">
                <span class="calculator-result-label">
                    Monthly contribution needed
                </span>

                <strong
                    class="calculator-result-value"
                    id="monthlySavingsNeeded"
                >
                    —
                </strong>

                <small id="monthlySavingsDescription">
                    Estimated contribution at the end of each month
                </small>
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-result">
                <span class="calculator-result-label">
                    Total future contributions
                </span>

                <strong
                    class="calculator-result-value"
                    id="totalFutureContributions"
                >
                    —
                </strong>

                <small>
                    New money added after today
                </small>
            </div>

            <div class="calculator-result">
                <span class="calculator-result-label">
                    Estimated investment growth
                </span>

                <strong
                    class="calculator-result-value"
                    id="estimatedSavingsGrowth"
                >
                    —
                </strong>

                <small>
                    Portion of the goal supplied by estimated returns
                </small>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="calculator-explanation">
            <h2>How this savings goal calculator works</h2>

            <p>
                The calculator first estimates how much the current savings
                may grow. It then calculates the monthly contribution needed
                to cover the remaining amount by the end of the selected
                period.
            </p>

            <div class="formula-grid">
                <div class="formula-card">
                    <span>Projected current savings</span>

                    <code>
                        Current savings × (1 + monthly rate)^months
                    </code>
                </div>

                <div class="formula-card">
                    <span>Monthly contribution needed</span>

                    <code>
                        Remaining goal ÷ contribution growth factor
                    </code>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>
                Monthly contributions are assumed to be added at the end
                of each month. The return should represent the expected
                annual return after investment fees.
            </p>

            <p>
                Enter the goal in future dollars. The
                <a href="/tools/inflation/">Inflation Calculator</a>
                can help estimate the future cost of something priced today.
                The
                <a href="/tools/investment-fee/">Investment Fee Calculator</a>
                can help illustrate how fees may affect long-term returns.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    {% include "components/planning-related-guide.njk" %}

    <p class="tool-disclaimer">
        For educational purposes only. Results are estimates and assume
        a constant return and regular end-of-month contributions. Actual
        returns, inflation, fees, taxes, and contribution timing may vary.
    </p>
</div>
